Class ImportCSVListener

java.lang.Object
  solidbase.core.CommandListener
      solidbase.core.ImportCSVListener

public class ImportCSVListener
extends CommandListener

This plugin executes IMPORT CSV statements. 

 IMPORT CSV INTO tablename
 "xxxx1","yyyy1","zzzz1"
 "xxxx2","yyyy2","zzzz2"
 GO
This plugin will transform the CSV lines into INSERT INTO tablename VALUES ("xxxx","yyyy","zzzz").
